14.Write a program to check if a year is leap year, and if leap, check if it’s a century year.

public class LeapYearAndCentury {
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		int year = 2026;

		if ((year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0) || year % 400 == 0) {
			System.out.println(year + " is a leap year.");

			if (year % 400 == 0) {
				System.out.println(year + " is a century year.");	
			} else {
				System.out.println(year + " is not a century year.");
			}
		} else {
			System.out.println(year + " is not a leap year.");
		}
	}
}


15.Write a program to check whether a number is even, and if even, check whether it’s greater than 50.

